      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver verified against at least one canonical benchmark with documented order-of-accuracy confirmation.",
      "rationale": "Fluent has published verification against lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmarks with second-order spatial convergence confirmed. Satisfies MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Discretization error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Grid convergence index (GCI) below 5% on hemolysis index QoI across all five operating points, with Richardson extrapolation applied to three systematically refined meshes.",
      "rationale": "Mesh refinement study performed on three grids (4.2 M, 8.7 M, 17.1 M cells). GCI values for the hemolysis index ranged from 3.8% to 9.4% across the five operating points; two high-shear operating points exceed the 5% threshold. Richardson extrapolation was applied but asymptotic convergence was not fully achieved in the impeller tip region. Achieved level 2 reflects incomplete convergence at the required spatial resolution; requiredLevel 3 is not met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
