      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental boundary conditions (inlet flow rate, outlet pressure, rotational speed) documented and matched to CFD inputs within stated measurement uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "FDA experimental dataset provides flow rate (±2%), pressure (±1%), and RPM (±0.5%) with full uncertainty characterization. CFD boundary conditions set to match nominal values; sensitivity runs confirm hemolysis index insensitive to boundary uncertainty at this level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
