      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) within ±25% of experimental values across all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values agree with FDA experimental data within ±18% at all five operating points. Systematic under-prediction of 8–12% at high-flow conditions is within acceptance band and consistent with literature. Exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
